{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a first-person horror game. You are trapped in a hedge maze at night with a ghost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Luckily, the creature is afraid of light and can be harmed by it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unluckily, there are only voice activated street lamps in the maze, and you have no other light sources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To escape, you'll need to explore the labyrinth, collect keys, and find the way out\u2014all while using the voice-activated lamps as your only weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">[Feature]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game captures your microphone audio volume, so shout loudly to control the lights and protect yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't worry if you don\u2019t have a microphone; there will be a control to make noise in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">[Playtime]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It will be a short horror experience lasting 20-40 minutes.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3307130?t=1731920463","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3307130?t=1731920463","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307130/8217ed1ccc3b99c8e95702e1ca9285f0fb4049bd/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731920463","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307130/8217ed1ccc3b99c8e95702e1ca9285f0fb4049bd/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731920463","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a first-person horror game. You are trapped in a hedge maze at night with a ghost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Luckily, the creature is afraid of light and can be harmed by it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">U